snippet.title: Narcicentric - Paradiddle Expert Song Playthrough
snippet.description:
We're taking a quick break from our drum cover videos by showcasing Paradiddle's note highway - our built-in rhythm game mode with custom song support and lots of customization options. Here's an Expert difficulty playthrough of one of 10 original songs we have in Paradiddle V1: Narcicentric by ElNeax.

Join our Discord community to never miss updates! https://discord.gg/paradiddle

VR drum cover played in Paradiddle: we're on Steam for PC VR (https://store.steampowered.com/app/685240/) or App Lab for Quest (https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3592251770823318/). This Can You Feel My Heart cover is specifically from our Version 1.0 update that's going to come out later this year.
